name: Robot Metropolis Carnival Series 10/10
description: The Robot Metropolis Carnival Series. Welcome! The beginning is the end and so what once was shall start anew. Enter the portal and loose your mind or find it again. Inside await you creations that you shall find nowhere else in the multiverse. The originator is the Dr. Prof. Kazimierz Maupa. His story shall be told another time. For now, enter, be well, and take care.
